{"tid":910893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基本法委員會委員劉迺強去世　友指患癌多年：既突然又不突然","createTime":"2018-11-21T13:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T01:58:54.000Z","uid":39464,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d1dd78828c37441633b6db0935f5f60a87cedb51","tid":910893,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"本報獲悉，今年6月獲全國人大常委會續任基本法委員會港方委員的劉迺強去世，終年71歲。劉迺強認識多年的港區人大代表蔡素玉向《明報》證實消息，她向本報表示，劉迺強患癌症多年，經歷多次手術和化療，形容消息「既突然又不突然」，透露數星期前曾與對方見面，「一齊飲茶」，當時對方剛做完手術不久，身體較弱，但仍關心社會大事，又思考如何幫助年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00001/1542806013919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00001%2F1542806013919&d=sg4kdzOBGnbgirfSeSyDw2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=fdb5ac9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00001%2F1542806013919&h=dae4fdfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00001/1542806013919</a>"},{"pid":"c6f8fc2411e90ea7b4e82d513612608fec826078","tid":910893,"uid":35221,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://chkp.org/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/%E7%86%B1%E7%83%88%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%88%E7%90%B4%E7%86%B1%E7%83%88%E5%9C%B0%E5%94%B1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchkp.org%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2583%2588%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%2590%25B4%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2583%2588%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2594%25B1.jpg&h=d7ba9ab1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c48211ff36c56af78ce039f02fd444da24e03f85","tid":910893,"uid":81113,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:16:25.000Z","msg":"基本法成為歷史文件未？"},{"pid":"c06c9dae74be2d7ff214dcb5bac8f0e7974cb5df","tid"